actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Public Works.

official_title: A bill to name the recently completed Federal Office building in West Palm Beach, Florida, the "Paul G. Rogers Federal Building".

summary.text: Names the recently completed Federal office building in West Palm Beach, Florida, the Paul G. Rogers Federal Building. Provides for the designation of such building by such name in any law, regulation, map, document, or record of the United States in which such building is referred to.
